7:["$","p","p-5",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Critical distinction"}],": L2 requires constant human monitoring (Tesla crash liability sits with driver); L4 does not require the human to respond. This legal boundary is central to liability frameworks."]}]
